                    for <span class="fst-italic fw-bolder">VBA desktop automations</span> and development of <span class="fst-italic fw-bolder">PowerBI dashboards</span> on local and global level within finance/payroll
                    departments.
                    If you would like to find out more about my experience- please check my <a href="#" class="fw-bolder text-secondary">project portfolio</a> and <a href="#" class="fw-bolder text-secondary">online resume</a>.
